    List<Integer> result = new ArrayList<>();
    result.addAll(numbers);
  }' The Use Arrays.asList() to wrap arrays option allows to report arrays, even if the bulk method requires a collection. In this case the quick-fix will automatically wrap the array in 'Arrays.asList()' call. New in 2017.1

